{"tid":623210,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"做完assignment拎比人抄真係賤撚過雞","createTime":"2018-04-09T20:11:43.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-19T01:50:07.000Z","uid":41491,"like":43,"dislike":49,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"7d50450463b35be93071f22eed26e162f96ce105","tid":623210,"uid":41491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T20:11:43.000Z","msg":"做雞都話有錢收<br />\n比份assignment人抄就咩都冇<br />\n自己做assignment就做到隻狗咁<br />\n人地一句唔該就諗都唔洗諗抄撚哂佢<br />\n大撚把時間吃喝玩樂打機溝女<br />\n已經唔係話想掉返轉<br />\n大佬一齊做都好呀<br />\n有唔識可以互相討論吓<br />\n屌<br />\n啲同學全撚部懶撚到閪咁<br />\n又唔撚上堂乜撚都唔識<br />\n臨midterm考試又要我講返教咗啲乜<br />\n見我毒撚唔撚識拒絕人就利撚用我<br />\n屌嬲<br />\n好撚後悔讀間辣殺大學識到啲咁嘅人<br />\n<br />\n屌 講完又返去做份assignment比人"},{"pid":"bf89142d3b375a319f4fd6ce2eb7cc0bd6e4cb17","tid":623210,"uid":137233,"like":46,"dislike":0,"score":46,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T20:18:04.000Z","msg":"傻閪自己攞嚟受<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b39a30ca27032c2c7ceaec6edc21ae59a873d6b","tid":623210,"uid":126897,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T20:25:56.000Z","msg":"拒絕人有幾難?"},{"pid":"82e633933e79e6369554080939967d5df3b3b005","tid":623210,"uid":166490,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T20:29:31.000Z","msg":"話自己未做咪得 deadline前先sd出黎話岩岩搞掂"},{"pid":"e85fede5eedae0e4cbae38c5ed07c3085ea08e0b","tid":623210,"uid":27915,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T20:32:57.000Z","msg":"樓主毒撚唔識拒絕，又妒忌人哋mk有得去玩，跟本自己攞嚟。"},{"pid":"10b41f8575390e913dc98f423e8314d97e36e8a4","tid":623210,"uid":82917,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T20:44:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/asset